# SURI of the faucet that funds new player burner wallets on first use.
#
# Default (//Alice) only works on a local revive dev node. On public Paseo
# Asset Hub, //Alice has been drained. //Bob (and other well-known dev keys)
# still have a balance there today and work as a quick override:
#   VITE_FAUCET_SURI=//Bob
# That's fine for ad-hoc verification but every other dev sharing this
# starter will also race for the same pool. For sustained use, paste the
# mnemonic from ~/.cdm/accounts.json (the same account `dot init` funded
# for contract deploy) — every new player costs ~1 PAS, watch its balance.
#
# Format: 12/24-word BIP39 mnemonic, optionally followed by a derivation path.
#   12-word-mnemonic ...
#   12-word-mnemonic ...//some/path
#   //Alice                    (uses the well-known dev phrase)
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and uncomment:
# VITE_FAUCET_SURI="<your mnemonic here>"
